  {
    "key": "1c4774c43c5cd5fff724ea5ae1bac1c5443c5c759064953c555642051e74b74b",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_09.png[/img]A shrill cry pierces the doldrums of the swamp. You rush forward and find a man thrashing about in the waters, his arms swinging ropes of kudzu. The water is foaming and bubbling and the snout of a dog briefly appears and spends that second barking for help instead of breathing for any momentary extension of life. Seeing you, the dog's owner calls out.%SPEECH_ON%Please, help! Something's got my dog!%SPEECH_OFF%",
